sentence.text: Results on CcO composition in tissues from adult animals and the review of data from recent literature strongly suggest that mitochondrial electron transport, NADH to ubiquinone is not a 14th subunit of CcO but may represent an assembly factor for CcO or supercomplexes (respirasomes) in mitochondria of growing cells and cancer tissues
